==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Manganese steel
<hw>Man`ga*nese" steel</hw>. <def>Cast steel containing a considerable
percentage (10-14) of manganese, which makes it very hard and tough and
highly resistant to wear. See <er>Alloy steel</er>, above.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Manganesian</ent>⟦br⟧
